lore the Seoul system. This ship was still under Drezzel''s command following the Battle of Endor and Emperor Palpatine''s death. Drezzel continued to serve the Empire under an Imperial Governor. However, the ship and Drezzel were destroyed during an accident involving the native Seoularian crystals.','Sienar Fleet Systems IF-120 Landing Craft 1.jpg',NULL,'Source text CC-BY-SA 3.0 from http://d6holocron.com/wiki/Imperial%20Landing%20Force%20Ship','["http://d6holocron.com/wiki/Imperial%20Landing%20Force%20Ship"]',13282,27096);
